ol]]{{citation needed|date=February 2015}} * [[National Association of Mutual Insurance Companies]]<ref name=civil/> * [[National Beer Wholesalers Association]]<ref name=WB4911>{{cite web|url=http://www.alec.org/AM/Template.cfm?Section=Private_Sector_Executive_Committee2 |title=ALEC &#124; Private Sector Executive Committee |publisher=Web.archive.org |date= |accessdate=October 27, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110409132834/http://www.alec.org/AM/Template.cfm?Section=Private_Sector_Executive_Committee2 |archivedate=April 9, 2011 }}</ref> * [[National Cable and Telecommunications Association]]<ref name=sd/> * [[National Coalition for Safer Roads]]<ref name=4DF/>{{Failed verification|date=July 2013}} * [[National Federation of Independent Business]]<ref name=civil/> * [[National Pawnbrokers Association]]<ref name=WB4911/> * [[National Popular Vote Inc.|National Popular Vote]]<ref name=4DF/> * [[National Rifle Association]]<ref name=riz /> * [[NetChoice]]<ref name=sd/> * [[News Corporation]] (parent company of [[Twentieth Century Fox]], [[Wall Street Journal]] and [[Fox News]])<ref name=sd/> * [[Novartis]]<ref name=riz /> * [[Cellmark|Orchid Cellmark]]<ref name=4DF/> * [[Pacific Research Institute]]<ref name=civil/> * [[Pfizer]]<ref name="Board of Directors" /><ref name=riz /> * [[PhRMA]]<ref name="Board of Directors" /> * [[Pickle Consulting Group]]<ref name=civil/> * [[Pioneer Institute]]<ref name=minnpost /> * [[Price Waterhouse Coopers]]<ref name=civil/> * [[Progress and Freedom Foundation]]<ref name=sd/> * [[Property Casualty Insurers]]<ref name=civil/> * [[Reason Foundation]]<ref name=sd/> * [[Reckitt Benckiser Pharmaceuticals]]<ref name=4DF/> * [[Sanofi Aventis]]<ref name=riz /> * [[Satellite Broadcasting and Communications Association]]<ref name=sd/> * [[Schering Plough]]<ref name=riz /> * [[Serlin Hale]]<ref name=4DF/>{{Failed verification|date=July 2013}} * [[Sprint Nextel]]<ref name=sd/> * [[State Farm Insurance]]<ref name="Board